title: Woman as Decoration
creator: Emily Burbank
description: LibriVox recording of Woman as Decoration, by Emily Burbank. Read by lots of LibriVox ladies: Julie VW, Neeru Iyer, Lee Ann Howlett, Elli, Ruth Golding, Tricia G, Cori Samuel, Jennifer Stearns, Jc Guan, Miriam Esther Goldman, Laurie Anne Walden, and Esther. A guide for women to complement their dress to their surroundings, be it in their own home, on outings or on stage. (Summary by Julie VW) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
